"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.9.3\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.9.3</span> 標題：斧頭、錛（axe, adze）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּרְזֶל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： barzel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:5\">DEU 19:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:5\">2KI 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:6\">2KI 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:34\">ISA 10:34</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： גַּרְזֶן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： garzen)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:5\">DEU 19:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:19\">DEU 20:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:7\">1KI 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:15\">ISA 10:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַעֲצָד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ma‘atsad)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:3\">JER 10:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： קַרְדֹּם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： qardom)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:48\">JDG 9:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:20\">1SA 13:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:21\">1SA 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:5\">PSA 74:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:22\">JER 46:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἀξίνη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： axinē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:10\">MAT 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:9\">LUK 3:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： πέλεκυς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： pelekus)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:13\">LJE 1:13</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0330_adze.jpg\" alt=\"木柄錛\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">木柄錛 (Metropolitan Museum of Art, CC0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>斧或錛是一種帶有鋒利金屬刃的工具，金屬頭固定在一根木柄上，約為一個男子手臂的長度。木柄通常會牢牢楔入金屬頭上的一個孔內，孔和刃分別位於金屬頭的兩端，若用繩子纏繞金屬頭和手柄，可使其更加牢固。斧（<em>garzen</em> ）的刃與手柄平行，而錛（<em>qardom</em> ）的刃則垂直於手柄。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0331_axe.jpg\" alt=\"敘利亞和伊朗的各種青銅套筒斧頭和錛頭（公元前2-1千年，聖安東尼奧藝術博物館（San Antonio Museum of Art），近東藏品）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">敘利亞和伊朗的各種青銅套筒斧頭和錛頭（公元前2–1千年，聖安東尼奧藝術博物館（San Antonio Museum of Art），近東藏品） (© Zereshk, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>這種工具用來砍伐樹木和木本植物，將其劈成小塊，也是木匠用來砍削木材的工具之一。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:13\">LJE 1:13</a> 中提到的「斧子」很可能是一種武器而非手工工具。雖然斧子的形狀一般是相同的，但有些語言會用不同的詞語表示用來工作的斧子和用作武器的斧子。另外，翻譯者也可以比較寬泛地翻譯這節經文的前半部分，例如譯成「有時候他們拿著武器」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
